A minimalistic illustration of two abstract human silhouettes facing each other across a sleek testing dashboard interface, represented by clean geometric shapes - circles, squares, and flowing lines in Salesforce's signature blue and cloud white palette. The figures are connected by intersecting curved pathways suggesting data flow and interaction patterns. The composition features generous white space, subtle drop shadows, and a sense of synchronized movement between the two entities, conveying parallel testing journeys merging at key validation points.
